Risk Disclosures

Investing involves risk, including potential for loss.Diversification and Asset allocation do not assure a profit or protect against a loss.Bonds are subject to interest rate risk and may decline in value due to an increase in interest rates.
An investment in the Money Market Fund is not insured or guaranteed by the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation or any other government agency. Although the Fund seeks to preserve the value of your investment at $1.00 per share, it is possible to lose money by investing in the Fund.
 



 
