MUTUAL FUNDS
Open an Account
State Farm™ offers convenient options once you decide it's time to open a new mutual funds account.
 


Apply Online
Online application

The minimum initial investment per fund is $1,000 (minimum initial investment amount does not apply to Tax Qualified Transfer or Rollover money).
Subsequent investments, including an Automatic Investment Plan (AIP), require a minimum investment of $50 per transaction per fund. Learn more about the Automatic Investment Plan.
Note: When using our electronic application, you will be asked to create a temporary ID and password to establish the account. Once the new mutual funds account is open, it will be available for viewing by logging in to your State Farm account within two business days. If you do not already have an ID and password with State Farm, it will be available for viewing by logging in to your State Farm account within two business days. If you do not already have an ID and password with State Farm you will be required to register with your new account number before accessing it online. For any questions, please call our Mutual Funds Response Center at 1-800-447-4930 between 8:00 am – 6:00 pm CT, Monday through Friday.

 


